Interface EntryLoader<K,​V>

Type Parameters:

All Superinterfaces:

All Known Subinterfaces:
EntryStore<K,​V>
public interface EntryLoader<K,​V>
extends MapLoader<K,​EntryLoader.MetadataAwareValue<V>>
This is an extension to MapLoader. Entries loaded by EntryLoader may have expiration times attached to them. In that case, the entry is removed after given expiration time. See MapLoader.
